A karo na 14, Grant Anderson ya ci nasara, kuma Frazier Climo ya yi wa Ayr kwallo, amma an ba wa ɗan wasan Scotland mai suna Rory Hughes katin ja, kuma an ba shi kyautar don wasan Warriors, hakan ya sa Melrose ya yi amfani da damar da aka samu don ya ci nasara kuma Jason Baggot ya ci nasara.
