Amma 'yan wasan gida sun dawo, kuma sa'ad da aka ba Struan Hutchinson katin ja don ya yi wa Climo wasa a lokacin da yake riƙe da ƙwallon, daga wasan da aka yi a wasan, MacPherson ya ci gaba da yin wasan bayan Ayr.
