Masu zanen kaya Valentino da Thom Browne sun yi jerin manyan tukwane don tarin SS19 da suka sa mutane suka yi farin ciki a bikin Paris Fashion Week.
Instagram tana cike da takalma na bazara da ba a saba gani ba, kuma waɗannan ƙwararrun sun nuna ƙirarsu a kan filayen da masu salo ke tafiya.
