Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar, in ji masana kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 ne aka kai ƙarar mutane 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka na cututtuka ne na cutar, kuma hakan ya sa yanayin ya zama da wuya.
A wasu yankunan ƙasar Sin, cutar HIV tana yaduwa da sauri domin an zubar da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da wannan cutar ya ragu kuma ya kusan ƙarewa, kamar yadda ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya suka faɗa a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
