A ranar Asabar, Rep. Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin da ake yi mata cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya saka bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dokoki uku na Jam'iyyar Republican a shafukan Wikipedia.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat a birnin Los Angeles ya ce, 'yan jarida da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na 'yan jarida ne ke sa a yi irin wannan jawabin.
A shafinsa na Twitter, Waters ya ce: "Wannan ƙarya ce, ƙarya ce mai kyau.
An ce a cikin bayanan da aka ba su, an haɗa da adiresoshin gida da kuma lambobin tarho na 'yan majalisar dattijai na Amirka Lindsey Graham na jihar South Carolina, da kuma Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu daga jihar Utah.
An wallafa wannan bayanin a Intane a ranar Alhamis, a kan babban birnin ƙasar Amirka, a lokacin da majalisar dattijai ta saurari karar wani mutum mai suna Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafin 'yan Adam.
