Johnny English Strikes Again - Wani fim mai ban tsoro da Rowan Atkinson ya yi
A yau, ana ganin muhimmancin Brexit a kowane sabon fim daga ra'ayin Britaniya kuma yana da kyau a sake farfado da wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English na spoof franchise - wanda ya fara a 2003 ta Johnny English kuma ya sake tashi a 2011 ta Johnny English Reborn.
Shin yin amfani da wannan hanyar ba da shawara ba zai zama sabon zarafi ga mutanen da suke tura abubuwa zuwa ƙasashen waje ba?
Ko da yaya yanayin yake, Johnny English mai launin fata, ya sami lasisinsa na yin amfani da shi a karo na biyu - sunan da ya ba da ya nuna cewa yana yin ba'a game da raunin da ba a yi wa masu kallon fina-finai ba.
Wannan ƙwararrun ɗan teku ne da ya yi amfani da Clouseau, da Mr Bean, da kuma ɗan ƙaramin ɗan'uwansa a wasan kwaikwayo na gasar Olympics na shekara ta 2012 a birnin London.
Da farko, ta yi koyi da Atkinson, wani matafiyi da kuma ɗan ƙasa da aka yi amfani da shi a cikin wani tallan talabijin da aka manta da shi na Barclaycard, kuma ta bar matsaloli a wurin da ta wuce.
Akwai abu ɗaya ko biyu da ya sa na yi farin ciki.
Ina son Johnny English ya zo kusa da jirgi mai saukar ungulu da ya saka tufafin soja da suka saba da shi kuma ya yi amfani da su wajen lalata gidansa.
An nuna kyautar Atkinson na yin wasan kwaikwayo, amma a cikin wani labari mai ban dariya ba shi da ban dariya kuma ba shi da muhimmanci, musamman tun da fina-finai masu wuya kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu suna nuna cewa wasan kwaikwayo yana da muhimmanci.
Kamar dai ana yin dariya ne ga yara ba manya ba, amma a ganina, baƙar magana ta Johnny English ba ta nuna hali mai kyau da kuma sha'awa kamar fina-finai marasa sauti na Atkinson game da halin Bean.
Ruwan sama na sihiri ya nuna cewa a yau ƙasar Biritaniya tana cikin matsala.
Wani ɗan kwamfuta mai suna Hacker ya ɓata sunan 'yan leƙen asiri na ƙasar Birtaniya, ya ba da sunayen dukan 'yan leƙen asiri na ƙasar, kuma hakan ya sa 'yan leƙen asiri suka yi mamaki - abin baƙin ciki Kevin Eldon bai taka rawa ba.
Ka yi la'akari da firaministan da yake ɗaukaka kansa a matsayin babban mai jefa ƙuri'a da kuma mai tsananin ƙarfi, amma ya zama gwauruwa a siyasa: Emma Thompson tana ƙoƙari ta yi koyi da irin wannan halin Teresa-May amma ba a rubuta kome game da ita ba.
Masu ba da shawara sun yi masa ba'a kuma suka ce zai ɗauki ɗan haya don ya je ya ɗauki ɗan haya.
Wannan yana nufin cewa Johnny English mai ban mamaki ne, wanda yanzu aka ɗauke shi aiki a matsayin mai koyarwa a makarantar sakandare, amma koyarwa ba tare da an rubuta shi ba hanya ce ta ɓoye abin da ya faru: fina-finai masu ban sha'awa kamar yadda English ya yi alkawarin makarantar sakandare ta takwas ta Rock.
An kai English zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa kuma ya sadu da abokinsa mai haƙuri Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya taka rawa.
Yanzu da yake Bough ya yi aure, an ba shi aikin sarrafa jirgin ruwa, aikin yarinya mai wahala da Vicki Pepperdine ke ɓata lokaci.
Saboda haka, Batman da Robin, waɗanda suka saba yin kuskure a cikin Sirrin Maɗaukakin Sarki, sun dawo da ƙarfi, suna haɗuwa da Ophelia Bulletova, mai kyau Olga Kurylenko.
Sa'ad da firaministan ya faɗa cikin tarkon mai haɗari na mai tallata harsuna da kuma fasahar harshe mai sauƙi, wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na ƙasar Britaniya: Jason Volta, mai ba da labari mai ban tsoro, ya yi wa Jake Lacy rawa.
English da Bough sun soma wasan kwaikwayo na dare da zai sa ka yi dariya, suna yin kamar masu kula, suna ƙona wuta a gidan abinci na Faransa; suna yin laifi da yawa don shiga cikin jirgin ruwa mai daraja na Volta; kuma English ya fara tashin hankali sa'ad da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da belun kunne na Virtual Reality don ya san abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
An bar dukan abubuwan da ake sha domin wannan taron na ƙarshe, amma duk da abokantaka da tashin hankali, akwai TV na yara a cikinsa.
Hakika, ba haka yake ba.
