Sakataren Kasuwanci na Burtaniya Greg Clark ya ce, "da a ce Birtaniya ta yi nasara a masana'antar kera motoci bayan Brexit, za ta yi nasara sosai.
Ya ƙara da cewa, "abin da ya fi damun mutane shi ne cewa Toyota ta gaya wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta bar Tarayyar Turai ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba, za ta dakatar da samar da kayayyakin a masana'anta a Burnaston, kusa da Derby.
Mista Clark ya ce: "Muna bukatar mu yi yarjejeniya.
Wani mai kera motoci a ƙasar Japan ya ce, idan Birtaniya ta yi watsi da yarjejeniyar da aka yi da ita, za a yi ta rasa aikin yi.
A cikin shekara ta 2015 ne aka yi kusan motoci 150,000 a tashar Burnaston, wadda ke yin na'urar Toyota mai suna Auris da Avensis, kuma an sayar da kashi 90 cikin 100 na waɗannan motoci a ƙasashen da ke cikin Ƙungiyar Tarayyar Turai.
Marvin Cooke, manajan kamfanin Toyota a birnin Burnaston ya ce: "Ina ganin idan Birtaniya ta bar Tarayyar Turai a ƙarshen watan Maris, za mu ga an daina yin kayayyaki a masana'antarmu.
Wasu masana'antun kera motoci a Burtaniya sun nuna damuwa game da ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai ba tare da sun amince da yadda za a yi amfani da wannan tsarin ba, ciki har da Honda, BMW, da Jaguar Land Rover.
Alal misali, kamfanin BMW ya ce zai yi wata ɗaya yana gina mini a birnin Oxford bayan Brexit.
Babban abin da ke damun masana'antun motoci shi ne haɗarin da ke tattare da kayayyaki idan ba a amince da ficewar Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai ba.
A lokacin, Toyota tana samar da kayayyaki da yawa, kuma a kowane minti 37 ana samun kayayyakin mota daga masu sayar da kayayyaki a Burtaniya da kuma ƙasashen Turai don a yi amfani da su.
