Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Jami'ai sun ce mutane 384 ne suka mutu a lokacin da wata girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku a birnin Palu da ke ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai ƙaru a tsawon lokaci.
Da yake babu hanyar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya sanin yanayin Donggala ba, da ke arewacin Palu kuma kusa da inda girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta auku.
Bayan wannan guguwar, an ƙaura da mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu.
Wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi su ne:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, kuma a shekara ta 2017 da aka yi hakan, mutane 379,800 ne suke zaune a yankin.
A lokacin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami, birnin ya cika shekara 40 yana wurin.
Donggala yana kan gabar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi kuma ya fi nisan mil 300.
Wannan yanki ne mafi girma a lardin kuma a shekara ta 2017 yawan mutanen da ke wurin sun kai 299,200.
Masunta da kuma noma suna da muhimmanci a yankin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin da ke kusa da gabar Donngala.
Ana yin hakar Nickel a wannan lardin, amma a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi, ne ake yin hakan.
A cewar Hukumar Taimako ta Indonesia, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donngala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya sake addabar yankin yammacin Donggala kuma ya kashe mutane tara.
A ƙasar Indonesia, girgizar ƙasa tana da yawa kuma a can girgizar ƙasa tana faruwa sau da yawa.
Wasu girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarun baya-bayan nan sun haɗa da:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta afku a gabashin gabashin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a yankunan da ke gabashin Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris da kuma farkon watan Afrilu, an yi girgizar ƙasa da yawa a gabar yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, da ke kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta yi girgizar ƙasa a kudu da tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibiri mafi yawan mutane a Indonesia.
A shekara ta 2009: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.6 a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
A shekara ta 2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.5 ta yi girgizar ƙasa a tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi na mita 10, wanda ya halaka birane da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: A yankin Pidie Jaya da ke ƙarƙashin yankin Aceh, an yi girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani, kuma hakan ya ɓata abubuwa da yawa kuma ya sa mutane tsoro don sun tuna da abin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka yi a shekara ta 2004.
Babu tsunami a wannan lokacin, amma an kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa ta yi girgizar ƙasa a tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonesia kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500.
Wannan girgizar ta lalata dubban gidaje kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido cikin matsala na ɗan lokaci.
Ɗan Sara Palin na fari ya zargi cewa yana haddasa faɗa a iyali
