Wani rahoto na kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobi ta Florida ya nuna cewa yawan gurɓataccen ruwan teku ya ragu a yankunan da ke kusa da Tampa Bay.
Rahotanni daga FWC sun ce, a cikin ruwan teku akwai wasu wuraren da ake ganin gurɓataccen iska a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte, da kuma Collier.
An kiyasta cewa ruwan teku mai gurɓataccen yanayi yana da nisan mil 130 a bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudu da Lee.
An gano wasu wuraren da aka yi amfani da sigogin a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun da ke gundumar Hillsborough da kuma wasu wurare a makon da ya shige.
An sake ganin gurɓataccen ruwan teku a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya shige, an samu matsakaicin yanayi na gurɓataccen yanayi a bakin tekun gundumar Pinellas, yanayi mai zafi a kusa da gundumar Hillsborough, yanayi mai zafi a gundumar Manatee, yanayi mai zafi a bakin tekun gundumar Sarasota, yanayi mai zafi a gundumar Charlotte, yanayi mai zafi a gundumar Lee, da kuma yanayi mai zafi a gundumar Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun matsaloli a numfashi a cikin gidajen Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
Ba a samu wani rahoto game da matsalar numfashi a Arewa maso Yammacin Florida a makon da ya shige ba.
